Project 4 — Identify Patient Attrition Risk (Supervised Learning)

Patient attrition for appointments is the rate at which patients stop returning to a practice for ongoing care. 
Heavily driven by missed appointments, single no-shows, cancellationns

Goal: Predict whether a patient will miss an appointment or stop returining to a practice for ongoing care. 

Target
Attrition = Yes / No

Features
  Age
  Gender
  Schecule lead time
  Transportation (Yes/No)
  Employment status/ income
  Time conflict
  Work conflict
  Distance from home
  Health Perception
  Job satisfaction


Works in Orange because for a classification project you can compare:
  logistic regression
  decision tree
  random forest

Provides strong visuals for confusion matrices and ROC curves.
